  "body": "### Component\r\n\r\nForge\r\n\r\n### Describe the feature you would like\r\n\r\nThe test report from a `forge test --fail-fast` run is not very informative. It informs the user of the function that failed. But it omits EVM and console logs useful in figuring out how the failure occurred.\r\n\r\nIt'll be more useful if `--fail-fast` includes logs and maybe traces too.\r\n\r\n### Additional context\r\n\r\n_No response_",
